Glossary:
  - Person: Abu Bakr Dulaf b. Jahdar al-Shibli
    Description: famous Sufi of Baghdu,;. d.c. A.D. 945-6.
---
It is related that one day when Shibli came into the bazaar, the people said,
‘This is a madman.’ He replied： ‘You think I am mad, and I think you are
sensible; may God increase my madness and your sense !
